Mechanics Ideas
- Find random sharpening stone  sharpen metal weapon on it  get temporary damage boost
- Say prayers for some sort of buff
- Items can break and have to be fixed using similar material  can melt down items of a material to create ingot of that material
- Poison Arrows  sling bullets vs rocks
- Agility bonus when carrying less things. Gain Agility with every step you take.
- Strength bonus when more nutrition. Gain strength by walking with more heavy stuff
- Intelligence bonus when more rested? Gain Intelligence by reading books and killing things.
